---
layout: page
meta_title: Campaigns
meta_description: Who's raising money?
title: Campaigns
---

<main id="main" class="main flex flex-1 h-full flex-col focus:outline-none" tabindex="-1">
    <div class="container md:w-4/5 mx-auto justify-center text-center px-4 py-6 md:pt-16">
        <div class="md:w-4/5 lg:w-2/3 mx-auto justify-center text-center">
            <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold pb-2 lg:pb-6">Run a fundraising campaign</h1>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-700 pb-4">Lots of people are fundraising to help us feed the NHS. We've been blown away by the generosity and support of so many.</p>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-700 pb-4">Are you running a fundraising campaign? Let us know!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pb-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row mx-auto md:justify-center">
        <div class="md:px-2 flex justify-center">
            <a class="dbox-donation-button bg-blue-800 hover:bg-blue-900 transition-all ease-in-out duration-300 py-4 px-6 rounded-lg cursor-pointer text-white text-lg md:text-2xl flex justify-center items-center font-regular border-b-4 border-blue-900" href="/fundraising">
                <span class="font-medium">Add your fundraiser</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container md:w-4/5 mx-auto justify-center text-center px-4 py-6 md:py-16">
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold pb-2 lg:pb-8">Check out some of the amazing fundraisers below</h3>
        <ul class="flex flex-wrap justify-center">
            {% for campaign in data.fundraising.records %}
                <li class="w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/4 flex p-2 md:p-3">
                    <div class="border border-blue-800 rounded-lg flex-grow bg-white flex flex-col overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="flex justify-center items-center w-full">
                            <div class="bg-white bg-cover bg-center pb-golden w-full border-b border-blue-800" style="background-image: url('/images/campaigns/{{ campaign.fields["Name"] | slug }}.png')"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-4 flex flex-col flex-grow">
                            <h4 class="font-bold pb-2">{{ campaign.fields["Name"] }}</h4>
                            {% if campaign.fields["Goal amount"] %}
                                <div class="pb-2">
                                    <span class="bg-blue-100 rounded py-1 px-2">
                                        Goal: £{{ campaign.fields["Goal amount"] | thousands }}
                                    </span>
                                </div>
                            {% endif %}
                            {% if campaign.fields["Description"] %}
                                <p>{{ campaign.fields["Description"] }}</p>
                            {% endif %}
                        </div>
                        {% if campaign.fields["Website"] %}
                            <a target="" class="px-4 py-2 border-t hover:bg-blue-100 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out rounded-b-lg" href="{{ campaign.fields["Website"] }}">
                                <p class="text-sm">
                                    View campaign →
                                </p>
                            </a>
                        {% endif %}
                    </div>
                </li>
            {% endfor %}
        </ul>
    </div>
</main>